// Semantic direction:
// strøm_aggregering computes running statistics over continuous event streams.
// type_tumle divides time into fixed, non-overlapping vindu_størrelse intervals.
// type_skyve produces a result every skyve_skritt regardless of window boundaries.
// type_økt groups events separated by less than økt_inaktivitet_gap into one window.
// hendelsestid is the time embedded in the event data; behandlingstid is arrival time.
// vannmerke tracks the expected bound of event timestamps to decide when windows are complete.
// uorden_toleranse is how long to wait for late-arriving events before closing a window.
// strategi_begrenset_uorden advances the watermark by max(seen_ts) - uorden_toleranse.
// sen_data_policy_oppdater retroactively updates a closed window's aggregat when late data arrives.
// policy_sideutdata routes late records to a separate stream instead of silently dropping them.
// agg_distinct_antall estimates cardinality using HyperLogLog for large streams.
// trigger_type controls when partial window results are emitted before the window closes.
// trigger_tid_vindu fires a partial result every N milliseconds within the window.
// sammenslå_retrigger re-emits updated results each time new data arrives in an open window.
// statlig_rensing evicts window state that is no longer needed to prevent memory growth.
// strøm_sql exposes SQL-like syntax (tumle(), skyve(), OVER PARTITION BY) for streaming queries.

// Primitive flow:
// tumle 1-minutt sum: strøm
//   .tidsstempel_ekstraktor(e -> e.ts)
//   .vannmerke(strategi_begrenset_uorden, uorden=10sek)
//   .tumle_vindu(60sek)
//   .gruppert_etter(e -> e.bruker_id)
//   .agg_sum(e -> e.beløp)
//   .utdata_strøm   // ett resultat per (bruker, minutt) når vinduet lukkes
// økt-vindu: strøm
//   .økt_vindu(inaktivitet_gap=30sek, maks=10min)
//   .agg_antall -> antall_hendelser_per_økt
// sen data: hendelse ankommer etter vannmerke -> sen_data_policy
//   policy_sideutdata: rut til separat strøm for manuell analyse
// trigger_tid: tumle_vindu(5min).sammenslå_trigger(trigger_tid_vindu(10sek))
//   -> emit delresultat hvert 10sek -> emit endelig ved vindu-lukking

// This defines streaming aggregation: tumbling/sliding/session windows, watermarks,
// late data policies, aggregate functions including HyperLogLog, triggers, and streaming SQL.
